songs.lyrics:

Four-door [?] back-to-back

New hundreds growin' on trees
Seein' fiends with Cartiers
Rockin' David Robinson's, hoppin' trains

Now I'm wavin' Tecs out the Lex

songs.title: Medusa Plate
